# data pulled from coindesk manually
d.bit <- data.table::fread( "bit_usd.csv", data.table=F ) %>%
  janitor::clean_names()
d.eth <- data.table::fread( "eth_usd.csv", data.table=F ) %>%
  janitor::clean_names()

Plot Z-scores

# Plot
ggplot( d.crypto.1 ,
        aes(
          x=date,
          y=close_z,
          color=currency
        )) +
  
  # Basics
  geom_line()+
  
  scale_color_manual(values = RColorBrewer::brewer.pal( 11 , "Spectral")[c(1,3)]) +
  
  # Themes
  theme_light()
